          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Section 5(1): omit <amend.in quote="1">21(7) of the Births and Deaths Registration Act 1951</amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1">63 of the Births, Deaths, Marriages, and Relationships Act 1995</amend.in>.</text>
