                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">1</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>A child's  father who is not a guardian of the child just because of section 17(2) or (3) becomes a guardian of the child if his particulars are registered after the commencement of this section as part of the child's  birth information because he and the child's  mother both notified the birth as required by <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 9</citation></changeable> of the Births, Deaths, Marriages, and Relationships Registration Act 1995.</text>
