    <schedule id="DLM1049034" in.amend="false" irdnumbering="no" official="yes" prov-type="clause" schedule.heading.continue="no" toc="yes" type="schedule" bill.no="98" bill.type="government" stage="1" year="2007">
      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">4</label>
